title: 50 shades of rooster: Vietnamese artists celebrate new year
text:
50 shades of rooster: Vietnamese artists celebrate new year - VnExpress International Artist: Tomato Nguyen 50 shades of rooster: Vietnamese artists celebrate new year A unique collaborative project inspired by the colorful bird, the symbol of the new lunar year. 
To celebrate the Year of the Rooster, Killien Huynh, an illustrator from Ho Chi Minh City, started a collaborative project bringing a group of 50 artists together to create artworks inspired by the only bird of the Vietnamese 12-animal zodiac. 
Check out the wonderful collection on Behance . We've selected some of the best here for you. Artist: Danny Dao
